{
  "video_id": "m-6Al08LvDM",
  "title": "Turning Basketball Courts Into Works of Art",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1350.0,
      "end_time": 2430.0,
      "text": "[Dan] In a lot of neighborhoods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2430.0,
      "end_time": 4730.0,
      "text": "the public park is the center of the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5750.0,
      "end_time": 9990.0,
      "text": "and the basketball court is the center of that public park."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9990.0,
      "end_time": 12390.0,
      "text": "Oftentimes, these courts, they're in rough shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13250.0,
      "end_time": 15240.0,
      "text": "There's courts where either there's no lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15240.0,
      "end_time": 19200.0,
      "text": "or where there's large gaps and cracks in the court's surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19240.0,
      "end_time": 21869.0,
      "text": "There can be huge dips that would be unsafe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21870.0,
      "end_time": 23660.0,
      "text": "hazardous to play on."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23660.0,
      "end_time": 25750.0,
      "text": "So seein' all these courts across the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25750.0,
      "end_time": 28840.0,
      "text": "inspired me to renovate public outdoor basketball courts"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28840.0,
      "end_time": 29970.0,
      "text": "and collaborate with artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29970.0,
      "end_time": 32269.0,
      "text": "to create unique works of art for the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34190.0,
      "end_time": 37890.0,
      "text": "[Karo] I pretty much played at this court my whole life."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38460.0,
      "end_time": 38900.0,
      "text": "It was a no-brainer for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 38900.0,
      "end_time": 41500.0,
      "text": "Like, I jumped at the opportunity to be able to come down"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 43709.0,
      "text": "and help paint and give back to the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 43710.0,
      "end_time": 46543.0,
      "text": "(classical music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55560.0,
      "end_time": 57430.0,
      "text": "[Dan] Lincoln Park is a special court for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57430.0,
      "end_time": 60900.0,
      "text": "because I actually used to play here when I was in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60900.0,
      "end_time": 62800.0,
      "text": "All my siblings grew up playing on this court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62800.0,
      "end_time": 65203.0,
      "text": "and so this court's been a long time coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "The actual process of renovating the court"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 70170.0,
      "text": "typically takes about two weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70170.0,
      "end_time": 72170.0,
      "text": "and usually they'll hire a local contracting crew"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72170.0,
      "end_time": 75500.0,
      "text": "to do any crack fill or patch repair."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75500.0,
      "end_time": 76740.0,
      "text": "And then after they've done that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76740.0,
      "end_time": 79320.0,
      "text": "we come in once the court has been resurfaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79320.0,
      "end_time": 81669.0,
      "text": "to get the artwork down and be ready for lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85100.0,
      "end_time": 87679.0,
      "text": "Since starting Project Backboard three and a half years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87680.0,
      "end_time": 90280.0,
      "text": "we worked on over two dozen courts around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91770.0,
      "end_time": 92979.0,
      "text": "One of the most fun parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92980.0,
      "end_time": 95480.0,
      "text": "is working with community volunteers on the court painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95480.0,
      "end_time": 97650.0,
      "text": "You're gonna start at the tape line"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97650.0,
      "end_time": 99240.0,
      "text": "and we're gonna work our way backwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99240.0,
      "end_time": 100570.0,
      "text": "You know, the basketball court, for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100570.0,
      "end_time": 103920.0,
      "text": "was always a place where you learned to be an engaged citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103990.0,
      "end_time": 105100.0,
      "text": "It's where you met your neighbors"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105100.0,
      "end_time": 107390.0,
      "text": "and kind of got together for a common purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107400.0,
      "end_time": 109790.0,
      "text": "And I think, too often, people think of basketball courts"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109790.0,
      "end_time": 111480.0,
      "text": "as a nuisance, when really it is a spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111480.0,
      "end_time": 114180.0,
      "text": "that can really bring people and communities together."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 117560.0,
      "end_time": 120430.0,
      "text": "[Karo] Before this, it was cracks all over the court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 120430.0,
      "end_time": 123550.0,
      "text": "graffiti everywhere, definitely in bad shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123550.0,
      "end_time": 125570.0,
      "text": "Giving back to the community kind of speaks to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 125570.0,
      "end_time": 127240.0,
      "text": "because this is my first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127240.0,
      "end_time": 129210.0,
      "text": "kind of being involved in a project like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129210.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131240.0,
      "text": "and it definitely inspires other kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131240.0,
      "end_time": 132760.0,
      "text": "due to the fact that, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132760.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "the younger generation always looks up"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 135670.0,
      "text": "to the older generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135670.0,
      "end_time": 138683.0,
      "text": "They see you giving back, it will inspire them to give back."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 140660.0,
      "end_time": 141520.0,
      "text": "(basketball net swishing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141520.0,
      "end_time": 144110.0,
      "text": "Being able to step on a new renovated court is pretty dope."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144110.0,
      "end_time": 146170.0,
      "text": "You know, know it seems small, just a basketball court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146170.0,
      "end_time": 147378.0,
      "text": "but, you know, it's a lot more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147378.0,
      "end_time": 148630.0,
      "text": "Everyone comes out."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148630.0,
      "end_time": 149740.0,
      "text": "People get off work."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 149740.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "Got people who don't even live in New Rochelle"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 152720.0,
      "text": "who come over here to watch the games,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 152720.0,
      "end_time": 155803.0,
      "text": "so definitely just the little things helps out a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159450.0,
      "end_time": 161320.0,
      "text": "[Dan] This didn't start as an art project."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161320.0,
      "end_time": 163910.0,
      "text": "It didn't start as a way to bring art into parks."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163910.0,
      "end_time": 166370.0,
      "text": "But I think I recognize that it's really important"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166370.0,
      "end_time": 168470.0,
      "text": "for me to inspire and help others"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168470.0,
      "end_time": 169850.0,
      "text": "do this in their own communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169850.0,
      "end_time": 172600.0,
      "text": "You know, I want people to feel like"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172600.0,
      "end_time": 174110.0,
      "text": "I can make a difference in my community."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 174110.0,
      "end_time": 176320.0,
      "text": "Maybe I'm not painting an entire basketball court."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176320.0,
      "end_time": 177540.0,
      "text": "Maybe I'm just buying new nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 177540.0,
      "end_time": 178910.0,
      "text": "and hanging them when they fall down."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178910.0,
      "end_time": 180520.0,
      "text": "Maybe I'm just picking up the trash."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 180520.0,
      "end_time": 183440.0,
      "text": "You know, whatever it is, it's, if you care about your park,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183440.0,
      "end_time": 185820.0,
      "text": "you care about your basketball court, take care of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185820.0,
      "end_time": 187886.0,
      "text": "(basketball net swishing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187886.0,
      "end_time": 190719.0,
      "text": "(classical music)"
    }
  ]
}